OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FA bakery owner in Oxford says trade is
OL,7,Fdown by 50% at one of his sites since
OL,8,Fa congestion charge was introduced in
OL,9,Fparts of the city.
OL,11,FThe temporary congestion charge scheme
OL,12,Flaunched in six Oxford streets - Hythe
OL,13,FBridge Street, St Cross Road, St
OL,14,FClement's Street, Thames Street,
OL,15,FMarston Ferry Road and Hollow Way - in
OL,16,FOctober 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
