OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FCars with permits and all other
OL,7,Fvehicles can pass through the charge
OL,8,Flocations for free. Without a permit,
OL,9,Fdrivers have to pay a charge of #5 per
OL,10,Fday to pass through the six locations.
OL,12,FExemption permits are available for
OL,13,Fvarious groups - including for
OL,14,Fresidents, traders, carers and blue
OL,15,Fbadge holders.
OL,17,FA traffic filters trial covering the
OL,18,Fsame roads is planned to replace the
OL,19,Ftemporary congestion charge shortly
OL,20,Fafter the Botley Road reopens.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FEight months on from the
OL,7,Fimplementation of the congestion
OL,8,Fcharge, views are split among
OL,9,Fbusinesses about the impact of the
OL,10,Fcharge.
OL,12,FFraser Jones is the co-owner of
OL,13,FBarefoot Bakery, which has four sites
OL,14,Fin the Oxford area.
OL,16,FHe says that the branch on Dawson
OL,17,FStreet, Oxford, has seen a big
OL,18,Fdownturn in footfall.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FAlthough Mr Jones says it is possible
OL,7,Fto reach the bakery without passing
OL,8,Fthrough the congestion charge zones,
OL,9,Fhe says the alternative route requires
OL,10,Fa lengthy detour which puts many
OL,11,Fpeople off from visiting.
OL,13,FMr Jones said: "It's been huge (the
OL,14,Fimpact). Instantly from the day it
OL,15,Fstarted, we are 50% down in sales.
OL,17,F"Footfall numbers are reduced, they're
OL,18,Fdeclining every month, it's just
OL,19,Fgetting quieter and quieter."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FMr Jones said he's considering whether
OL,7,Fit's worth keeping the Dawson Street
OL,8,Fsite open.
OL,10,FHe said "It's a very student-populated
OL,11,Farea, there's lots of businesses
OL,12,Faround.
OL,14,F"It should be wonderful, we should
OL,15,Fhave footfall left, right and centre,
OL,16,Fbut it's just going down and down.
OL,18,FMr Jones added that the Kidlington
OL,19,Fbranch of his bakery, which is outside
OL,20,Fthe congestion charge zone, continues
OL,21,Fto grow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FMr Jones' concerns are echoed by Yola
OL,7,FDrage, who owns two Oxford restaurants
OL,8,Faffected by the charge.
OL,10,FShe said: "Five years ago, we had a
OL,11,Fvery vibrant street, more shops
OL,12,Ffronting the main area, but now some
OL,13,Fof them have closed already because of
OL,14,Fthe congestion charge.
OL,16,F"Always new businesses will crop up,
OL,17,Fbut as soon as the congestion charge
OL,18,Fwas introduced in October, we saw an
OL,19,Fimmediate effect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,F"Lack of traffic also meant lack of
OL,7,Fcustom."
OL,9,FHowever, Aeron Buchanan, who runs The
OL,10,FGallery bouldering centre, cafe and co-
OL,11,Fworking space in the city, is in
OL,12,Ffavour of the congestion charge and
OL,13,Fsaid it has benefitted his business.
OL,15,FHe said: "The congestion charge has
OL,16,Fnoticeably reduced the traffic around
OL,17,Four whole area, which has definitely
OL,18,Fmade it more pleasant.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,F"So it's now easier to walk around,
OL,7,Fit's easier to cycle around and it's
OL,8,Feven easier to drive around.
OL,10,F"We have seen our customer numbers
OL,11,Fincrease, there's increasing trend for
OL,12,Fus and we expect that to continue, and
OL,13,Foverall, it's a really positive thing."
OL,15,FMr Buchanan described the congestion
OL,16,Fcharge as a 'no-brainer' and said that
OL,17,Fsomething needed to be done to tackle
OL,18,FOxford's busy roads.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FHe continued: "It's just reducing
OL,7,Ftraffic, but not impeding people's
OL,8,Fability to get to us.
OL,10,F"Importantly, by reducing the traffic,
OL,11,Fthe majority of our customers who do
OL,12,Fcycle here, walk here, come by bus,
OL,13,Fit's much better for them, so we're
OL,14,Factually seeing a much bigger upside
OL,15,Fto any conceivable downside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,FIn a statement, Councillor Gareth
OL,7,FEpps, Oxfordshire County Council's
OL,8,FCabinet Member for Transport said: "It
OL,9,Fis clear that many businesses are
OL,10,Ffeeling significant pressures due to a
OL,11,Fnumber of local and national factors.
OL,13,F"Rising costs and economic uncertainty
OL,14,Fwere cited as the most common
OL,15,Fchallenges in the business survey
OL,16,Fconducted for us.
OL,26,@pD@dOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,F"The temporary congestion charge has
OL,7,Fbeen in place on six roads in Oxford
OL,8,Fsince 29 October to help reduce
OL,9,Ftraffic while Botley Road remains
OL,10,Fclosed and the traffic filter trial is
OL,11,Fdelayed.
OL,13,F"70 per cent of businesses surveyed
OL,14,Fsay the congestion charge has had no
OL,15,Feffect, or a positive effect on their
OL,16,Fbusiness.
OL,18,F"And nearly 80 per cent of respondents
OL,19,Fsaid that compared to a year ago,
OL,20,Ftheir performance is the same or
OL,21,Fbetter.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,F"However, we do know that some areas
OL,7,Fin the city are showing a decline in
OL,8,Fspend. Published credit and debit card
OL,9,Fspend data for monthly spending in the
OL,10,FSt Clements and Cowley Road area has
OL,11,Fdeclined between 2.9% and 13.5%
OL,12,F(nationally there has also been a
OL,13,Fdecline in spending).
OL,15,F"All car parking in the St Clements
OL,16,Fand Cowley Road area can be accessed
OL,17,Fwithout passing a congestion charging
OL,18,Fpoint.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781889574
OL,3,CBakery owner says trade has halved
OL,4,Csince congestion charge introduced
OL,6,F"There's still more to do to improve
OL,7,Ftravel in and around Oxford and enable
OL,8,Feveryone to get around more easily.
OL,9,FThe traffic filters trial, coming in
OL,10,Fthe autumn, is one way we'll further
OL,11,Freduce traffic and enable bus journeys
OL,12,Fto be quicker and more reliable.
OL,14,F"As the new portfolio holder for
OL,15,Ftransport, I'm keen to engage with
OL,16,Fbusinesses across the city and discuss
OL,17,Fhow we can make sure that Oxford
OL,18,Fremains an attractive place to live,
OL,19,Fwork, visit and do business."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
